divs: Sighting DetailsVideoing classified equipment for a major defense company, assignment to video incoming aircraft for the test at the top of a moutain - observed a bright disk just off course of the aircraft and thought it was an aircraft until it got close enought to recognize. I have the video on a DVD of the aircraft and the disc incoming for review. I want to remain annomous due to my work with the defense company. This was a classified range and no other aircraft were cleared to be in the area during this test. You can contact me for copy of the DVD if you want to view it.
Summary: Video in mid day slightly overcast - bright disc shape 400KMH.
